  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1038">
<l>ēriṉu naṉṟā meruviṭutal kaṭṭapi</l>
<l>ṉīriṉu naṉṟataṉ kāppu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Manuring is better than ploughing; after weeding, watching is better than watering (it).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
